				</div>
				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3>Can a neck lift be combined with other procedures?</h3>
					<p>Yes, neck lifts are commonly combined with facelifts, liposuction, <a href="https://www.theaesthetic.in/facelift-surgery-in-delhi/" title="Facelift Surgery">facelift procedures</a>, and other facial surgeries for comprehensive results. Combining procedures can enhance overall outcomes and reduce total recovery time.</p>
